title: Man-Cave | Watch: UFC fighter Johny Hendricks finds out he's having a little boy
text:
Former UFC Welterweight Champion Johny Hendricks made the news a few weeks ago when he failed to make weight for a fight.
It's never good when a fighter misses weight and it really, really pisses off UFC President Dana White.
But Johny got some awesome news when his wife breaks to him over dinner that they're having a little boy.
Nice end to a tough few weeks for the fighter.
